title: Haydn - Cello Concertos - Hogwood, AAM, Coin
description:
Haydn: Cello Concertos.

Joseph Haydn's Cello Concert No. 1 in C major and Cello Concerto No. 2 in D major, performed by Christophe Coin (cello) and the Academy of Ancient Music under Christopher Hogwood. These are masterful performances which will please even those who don't yet know that they can enjoy period instrument performances. (In addition, this CD holds the maximum possible amount of nostalgic value for me; it was the first classical music compact disc-back when we called them that-that I ever listened to, as a teenager...sigh.)
